            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Not necessarily. When two pages rank at positions 1 and 3 for the same keyword, that's SERP dominance — beneficial. Problems arise when competing pages suppress each other, pushing both to page 2 instead of securing one top position.</p></div></div>
          </div>
